{"tid":1785651,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"中國版《PES 2020》，由今天起删除有關奧斯爾的一切資料。","createTime":"2019-12-16T14:06:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-17T11:57:53.000Z","uid":41998,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"834c4da1859f2a0d0774e3f928bfe2060d99660d","tid":1785651,"uid":41998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T14:06:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w5jLShL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw5jLShL.jpg&h=15d73575&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大炎上！KONAMI「殺掉」奧斯爾<br />\n<br />\n「奧斯爾事件」繼續發酵，由日本遊戲公司Konami開發，網易遊戲代理的中國版《PES 2020》，由今天起删除有關奧斯爾的一切資料。<br />\n<br />\n消息已在Twitter日本用家中迅速傳開，有日本網民指「KONAMI是日本企業吧？雖然一直玩得很高興，但這次接受不了」、「中國真的太糟糕，比希特拉還要鬼畜」。<br />\n<br />\n又有日本網民向同胞解釋，外資公司進入中國市場後需要聘請一定數量共產黨員，有些事情不是母公司可控制。<br />\n<br />\n阿仙奴中場奧斯爾日前在社交網站貼文，聲援被中共打壓的東突厥斯坦地區的維吾爾人。<br />\n<br />\n大球場道<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10157895810142171&amp;id=167468312170\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D10157895810142171%26id%3D167468312170&d=dVEf9brN%2BTtwApumOSMW7sLrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=44b2d184\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10157895810142171&amp;id=167468312170</a>"},{"pid":"6f31cac19b9f4381d579ffa9984ab4b61d1869c7","tid":1785651,"uid":129988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T14:08:48.000Z","msg":"借po<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一屆「和你影」攝影比賽<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1785444\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1785444</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"92542032cc24309037021a04786101630d6fb2ec","tid":1785651,"uid":101392,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T14:10:01.000Z","msg":"大力推俾日本戰線<br />\n加速日版人權法！"},{"pid":"cb965f5a1132202c1a74978f98876e42b1596ae9","tid":1785651,"uid":202524,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T14:10:36.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 借個位黎<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">德國戰線要人</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">目標：5萬人聯署</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">依家差2萬人咋！！！</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n冇時間啦25號截止，極度要人幫手!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1782422\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1782422</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8564a90e5b2773d8b6938baf1e2b3d1a2782942f","tid":1785651,"uid":334806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T14:11:04.000Z","msg":"燒到埋身<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5021843c31762700f3180c31af72ad18157e383a","tid":1785651,"uid":200328,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T14:14:20.000Z","msg":"KONAMI呢間垃圾公司<br />\n本身就好撚銅臭好噁心, 遊戲界都算出晒名了<br />\n依家應該再臭出遊戲界外"},{"pid":"2f39be7c9ddcbb7a99eb8b76816381193df90d3c","tid":1785651,"uid":41998,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T14:18:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GBXBeAP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGBXBeAP.jpg&h=b3496a63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/st5GqHv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fst5GqHv.jpg&h=dcfaae82&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8309aa0d48d6d0000ba11e41f90e531193f3c3fd","tid":1785651,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T14:36:46.000Z","msg":"加速主義 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9